OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781953373
OL,3,CTwo trains collide near Bedford,
OL,4,Cclosing all lines as emergency
OL,5,Cservices respond
OL,7,FTwo trains have collided in
OL,8,FBedfordshire, with all services
OL,9,Fbetween Bedford and Luton cancelled as
OL,10,Femergency services respond.
OL,12,FImages from the scene appear to show
OL,13,Ftwo damaged East Midlands Railway
OL,14,F(EMR) trains still on the tracks. At
OL,15,Fleast one is a Luton Airport Express
OL,16,Ftrain, with passengers seen gathered
OL,17,Fin neighbouring fields.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
