OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781953373
OL,3,CTwo trains collide near Bedford,
OL,4,Cclosing all lines as emergency
OL,5,Cservices respond
OL,7,FBritish Transport Police said on
OL,8,Fsocial media: "We're responding to
OL,9,Freports of a collision involving two
OL,10,Ftrains in the Bedford area."
OL,12,FThere is currently no Thameslink
OL,13,Fservice running between Luton and
OL,14,FBedford, and Network Rail has urged
OL,15,Fpassengers to delay travelling.
OL,17,FEMR trains are "unable to run in or
OL,18,Fout of" London St Pancras for the rest
OL,19,Fof the day, the service said.
