OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781953373
OL,3,CTwo trains collide near Bedford,
OL,4,Cclosing all lines as emergency
OL,5,Cservices respond
OL,7,FIt added: "Customers are advised DO
OL,8,FNOT TRAVEL this evening".
OL,10,FHeidi Alexander said she was "deeply
OL,11,Fconcerned" by the reports.
OL,13,FIn a post on X, the transport
OL,14,Fsecretary said: "I'm deeply concerned
OL,15,Fto hear reports of the collision
OL,16,Finvolving 2 East Midlands Railway
OL,17,Fpassenger trains.
OL,19,F"I'm grateful to emergency services
OL,20,Fwho are on the scene, attending to
OL,21,Fthose affected.
