OL,3,CTwo trains collide near Bedford,
OL,4,Cclosing all lines as emergency
OL,5,Cservices respond
OL,7,F"We're working quickly with the rail
OL,8,Findustry and local partners to support
OL,9,Fpassengers."
OL,11,FBedfordshire Police said emergency
OL,12,Fservices are at the scene on a stretch
OL,13,Fof the railway just south of Bedford.
OL,15,F"All lines through the area have been
OL,16,Fstopped," the force said. "Please
OL,17,Fcheck your journey before you travel
OL,18,Fand allow plenty of extra time.
OL,20,F"We are asking for people to avoid the
OL,21,Farea and we will update when we can."
